title: Nuan Hun Qing Chong Qi
overview: The eldest young miss of the Mo family, Mo Shi Shi, was forced to leave her home, changing her name to Shi Yi, after her mother passed away.Her sister, Mo Jing Jing, killed her mother and loved Shen Mu Han.But Shen Mu Han loved Mo Sha Sha, another sister of the Mo family. He believed that Mo Shi Yi was the one who killed her, and decided to marry Mo Shi Yi to get revenge.One day, Mo Shi Yi wakes up and finds out that she traveled back in time to the day she married Shen Mu Han. What will happen next?
